 <i>This lie isn't</i>
 <i>very persuasive.</i>

00:12:53.601 --> 00:12:56.367 position:7% line:83% align:start
The reason the person involved
went to so much trouble

00:12:56.400 --> 00:12:58.934 position:16% line:83% align:start
is that if they succeeded
in killing him

00:12:58.968 --> 00:13:00.667 position:19% line:83% align:start
