00:14:24.334 --> 00:14:27.734 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Why did the killer need to</i>
 <i>create Steel Lady Nanase,</i>

00:14:27.767 --> 00:14:29.734 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and why use such</i>
 <i>a specific way</i>

