 <i>then work to make it</i>
 <i>so big that</i>

00:17:30.300 --> 00:17:32.701 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>it causes enough trouble</i>
 <i>for a detective to take action?</i>

00:17:32.734 --> 00:17:35.367 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Anonymous] <i>I can't see</i>
 <i>the pendulum thing happening.</i>

00:17:35.400 --> 00:17:37.234 position:10% line:89% align:start
Wait, the flow changed again.

00:17:37.267 --> 00:17:39.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
The solution may not
be realistic, but it's odd

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:43.133 position:7% line:83% align:start
that they'd change their minds
again so quickly.

00:17:43.167 --> 00:17:46.534 position:10% line:83% align:start
Didn't the flow just change,
because of Kuro's ability?

00:17:50.267 --> 00:17:52.100 position:16% line:83% align:start
Iwanaga, you said Rikka's
the one who's trying

00:17:52.133 --> 00:17:54.434 position:16% line:83% align:start
to give Steel Lady Nanase
a form, right?

00:17:54.467 --> 00:17:55.300 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:17:55.334 --> 00:17:57.367 position:35% line:83% align:start
And she has
the same ability as Kuro

00:17:57.400 --> 00:17:59.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
that allows her to choose
the future, doesn't she?

00:17:59.868 --> 00:18:02.334 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yes. As I said earlier.

00:18:02.367 --> 00:18:03.033 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:18:03.067 --> 00:18:04.334 position:33% line:83% align:start
But if then,
that's the case,

00:18:04.367 --> 00:18:06.934 position:21% line:83% align:start
Rikka can also force
the future she wants,

00:18:06.968 --> 00:18:08.100 position:27% line:89% align:start
just like Kuro...

00:18:08.133 --> 00:18:09.868 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yes. And that's exactly why

00:18:09.901 --> 00:18:12.534 position:27% line:83% align:start
the tides turned
so quickly again.

00:18:12.567 --> 00:18:16.234 position:16% line:83% align:start
The idea that this is all
caused by a ghost is popular.

00:18:16.267 --> 00:18:19.567 position:7% line:83% align:start
All she had to do was point out
a few flaws in our solution,

00:18:19.601 --> 00:18:21.067 position:30% line:89% align:start
then die once.

00:18:21.100 --> 00:18:24.968 position:13% line:83% align:start
And she could easily shift
the flow back in her favor.

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:27.901 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's entirely possible
that several of the posts

00:18:27.934 --> 00:18:30.067 position:35% line:83% align:start
are written
by Rikka personally.

00:18:31.534 --> 00:18:32.400 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ri...

00:18:33.434 --> 00:18:34.334 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:18:40.167 --> 00:18:43.100 position:19% line:83% align:start
This wiki site, despite
a sudden influx of traffic

00:18:43.133 --> 00:18:45.334 position:30% line:83% align:start
concurrent with
mass-posting by users,

00:18:45.367 --> 00:18:48.968 position:13% line:83% align:start
has somehow managed not to
completely crash its server

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:51.033 position:24% line:83% align:start
and we haven't run
into any trolls.

00:18:51.067 --> 00:18:54.067 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's not normal for
a net discussion, is it?

00:18:54.100 --> 00:18:57.000 position:19% line:83% align:start
So that means Rikka is
probably choosing the future

00:18:57.033 --> 00:19:01.000 position:16% line:83% align:start
with the fewest problems
while maintaining the site.

00:19:01.033 --> 00:19:03.968 position:16% line:83% align:start
She may not be censoring
our posts, but it's clear

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:06.267 position:33% line:83% align:start
that she has
the home-field advantage.

00:19:06.300 --> 00:19:08.834 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Rikka surpasses</i>
 <i>the laws of nature.</i>

00:19:08.868 --> 00:19:10.567 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Which means the way to</i>
 <i>solve this</i>

00:19:10.601 --> 00:19:11.868 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>hasn't changed at all.</i>

00:19:11.901 --> 00:19:13.534 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>In fact, because</i>
 <i>Rikka got a head start</i>

00:19:13.567 --> 00:19:17.067 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and had everyone believe</i>
 <i>that Steel Lady Nanase exists,</i>

00:19:17.100 --> 00:19:19.534 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>we're at a disadvantage.</i>

00:19:19.567 --> 00:19:21.033 position:16% line:89% align:start
This assembly is unique.

00:19:21.067 --> 00:19:24.100 position:35% line:83% align:start
After all,
the truth never existed here.

00:19:24.133 --> 00:19:26.133 position:19% line:89% align:start
This is simple fiction.

00:19:28.501 --> 00:19:29.300 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:19:30.267 --> 00:19:31.434 position:21% line:89% align:start
Both Rikka and I know

00:19:31.467 --> 00:19:35.133 position:19% line:83% align:start
that Steel Lady Nanase
didn't exist before.

00:19:35.167 --> 00:19:38.801 position:16% line:83% align:start
But Rikka is still trying
to give that fiction a form.

00:19:38.834 --> 00:19:40.234 position:35% line:89% align:start
Meanwhile,

00:19:40.267 --> 00:19:42.300 position:21% line:83% align:start
Kuro and I are trying
to convince everyone

00:19:42.334 --> 00:19:46.434 position:16% line:83% align:start
that what has manifested
in reality doesn't exist.

00:19:46.467 --> 00:19:47.367 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:19:57.167 --> 00:20:00.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
This is a committee
of dueling fictions!

00:20:02.801 --> 00:20:04.067 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:08.868 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Kotok]
I will claim victory.

00:20:08.901 --> 00:20:13.501 position:13% line:83% align:start
I've only used one solution
so far out of a total of four.

00:20:13.534 --> 00:20:16.834 position:13% line:83% align:start
All I need is for a portion
of the assembly to believe it.

00:20:16.868 --> 00:20:18.267 position:35% line:89% align:start
A portion?

00:20:18.734 --> 00:20:19.968 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>I see.</i>

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:21.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>The Internet is just</i>
 <i>a swirling mass</i>

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:23.968 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>of different viewpoints.</i>

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:25.834 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's not always easy</i>
 <i>for everyone</i>

00:20:25.868 --> 00:20:27.534 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>to believe in</i>
 <i>a single truth.</i>

00:20:27.567 --> 00:20:31.200 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>In that case, you need to</i>
 <i>have a variety of truths</i>

00:20:31.234 --> 00:20:34.467 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>enough to match up against</i>
 <i>the variation of views.</i>

00:20:34.501 --> 00:20:37.234 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>We couldn't completely</i>
 <i>dispel everyone's belief</i>

00:20:37.267 --> 00:20:40.167 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>in Steel Lady Nanase with</i>
 <i>the pendulum solution,</i>

00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:42.701 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>but at least a few of them</i>
 <i>should harbor some doubt now.</i>

00:20:42.734 --> 00:20:44.267 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Kuro grunt]

00:20:44.300 --> 00:20:48.100 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>And she's going to repeat</i>
 <i>this process three more times</i>

00:20:48.133 --> 00:20:51.367 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>to chip away at</i>
 <i>Steel Lady Nanase's support.</i>

00:20:51.400 --> 00:20:53.634 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even if she doesn't gain</i>
 <i>the majority,</i>

00:20:53.667 --> 00:20:56.133 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>she just has to make</i>
 <i>a large enough number of them</i>

00:20:56.167 --> 00:20:58.601 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>believe that</i>
 <i>Rikka's proposed bill</i>

00:20:58.634 --> 00:21:00.234 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>is not worth voting for.</i>

00:21:00.267 --> 00:21:03.200 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's why this strategy</i>
 <i>has a chance.</i>

00:21:05.767 --> 00:21:07.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>She's incredible.</i>

00:21:07.267 --> 00:21:10.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Using her knowledge</i>
 <i>to wield a blade in one hand</i>

00:21:10.200 --> 00:21:12.434 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>while subtly injecting</i>
 <i>poison with the other.</i>

00:21:12.467 --> 00:21:15.567 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Who'd think that someone</i>
 <i>who's chosen lies as weapons</i>

00:21:15.601 --> 00:21:17.267 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>could be so diabolical...?</i>

00:21:19.634 --> 00:21:23.667 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Nameless] <i>No! Steel Lady</i>
 <i>Nanase is totally a real ghost.</i>

00:21:23.701 --> 00:21:25.100 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>I've seen her!</i>

00:21:25.133 --> 00:21:27.734 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>She appeared in front of</i>
 <i>my car out of nowhere!</i>

00:21:27.767 --> 00:21:29.968 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>This happened five days ago.</i>

00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:32.400 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>She came out of smoke,</i>
 <i>went totally berserk</i>

00:21:32.434 --> 00:21:35.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and started swinging</i>
 <i>a huge steel beam at me!</i>

00:21:39.667 --> 00:21:40.567 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:21:41.601 --> 00:21:42.467 position:33% line:89% align:start
[sudden fear]

00:21:45.434 --> 00:21:48.734 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>That was a vengeful spirit.</i>
 <i>No doubt about it.</i>

00:21:48.767 --> 00:21:50.000 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I could've been</i>
 <i>killed by her,</i>

00:21:50.033 --> 00:21:51.601 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>just like</i>
 <i>that detective was!</i>

00:21:56.968 --> 00:21:59.033 position:21% line:89% align:start
I will be victorious.

00:22:12.901 --> 00:22:16.267 position:35% line:83% align:start
All right,
let solution two commence!

00:22:24.667 --> 00:22:29.033 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ending music]

00:23:54.200 --> 00:23:56.667 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>We deploy the second and</i>
 <i>third solutions</i>

00:23:56.701 --> 00:23:58.367 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>to defeat Steel Lady Nanase.</i>

00:23:58.400 --> 00:24:01.267 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Though Rikka Sakuragawa</i>
 <i>stands in our way.</i>

00:24:01.300 --> 00:24:04.367 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Will we be able to</i>
 <i>vanquish the ghost?</i>

00:24:04.400 --> 00:24:05.434 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Next time,</i>

00:24:05.467 --> 00:24:07.100 position:24% line:89% align:start
"Dueling Fictions."

